description:
When the sky turns hostile, only the fastest pilots survive.

In AirJet Fighter: Sky Assault, you're at the helm of a cutting-edge jet, flying into dangerous missions where every second counts. Engage in thrilling aerial combat, lock onto enemy aircraft, dodge incoming missiles, and unleash devastating firepower across dynamic landscapes. From open seas to city skylines, each battlefield challenges your reflexes and precision.

Upgrade your aircraft, customize your arsenal, and master multiple game modes—from story-driven campaigns to survival showdowns and timed strike missions. With smooth controls, immersive visuals, and adrenaline-pumping action, this isn’t just a flight—it’s an all-out sky assault.

Main Features:

-High-speed jet combat with smooth, responsive flight mechanics

-Campaign mode with progressive challenges and rewards

-Survival and Time Attack modes to test your skills under pressure

-Realistic 3D jet models and atmospheric battle zones


Take flight, dominate the skies, and write your legacy as an elite air combat pilot.
